# 🎧 boAt Lifestyle – Landing Page UI

This project is the **homepage UI** for the boAt Lifestyle website – built using only **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**. It features product categories, a hero banner, filtering system, and a responsive design for a premium shopping experience.

---

## 📁 Files

```plaintext
📂 project-rootboAt-project/
│
├── index.html            
├── login.html
├── signup.html
│
├── css/
│   ├── style.css         
│   ├── login.css         
│   └── signup.css        
│
├── js/
│   ├── main.js           
│   ├── login.js          
│   └── signup.js  
🖼 Features
✨ Hero section with CTA

🎧 Product categories & filters

🛒 Dynamic product grid

🧩 Responsive layout

🚀 Smooth scroll & animations

🧑‍💼 Login / Signup buttons (non-functional UI links)

🛠 How to Run
Download all three files (main.html, styles.css, script.js)

Place them in the same directory

Open main.html in your browser

No server or build tool required – it's 100% static front-end.

🚀 Preview
Sample product categories include:

Headphones

Earphones

Speakers

Smart Watches

Includes filters, pricing, product badges, and stylish cards.

